-- Bank Asya says reports on ending exclusive talks with QIB do not reflect truth
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Thu Jul 03, 2014 02:15AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 3 (Reuters) - Turkish Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> said on Thursday reports that exclusive talks had ended with Qatar Islamic Bank (QIB) <QISB.QA> over acquiring a stake in the Turkish lender did not reflect the truth.

